post_summaries.description: The Instagram post by drip_szn_collection features a collection of sports trading cards laid out on what appears to be a bed or soft surface. The cards are from the "Illusions Mega" set, and include images of football players. A text overlay on the image says "pulls from the illusions mega appreciate you my guy" and also has the text "Nice pulls! S/O @drip_szn_216 for the illusions mega!!"

The image shows a pair of Air Jordan 1 Hand Crafted sneakers with a white leather upper, multicolor leather, and Durabuck overlays. The post also includes hashtags related to sneakers, streetwear, and brands like Nike, Jordan, and Yeezy.
The image shows a pair of Air Jordan 1 High Bordeaux sneakers. The shoes have a white base with Bordeaux overlays and metallic silver Swooshes.
The image shows a Charizard GX Pokémon card displayed on a clear plastic stand.
The image is of a Japanese Pokemon card featuring Slowpoke and Psyduck as a "Tag Team" card. The post indicates the card is for sale.
The image shows a Giovanni's Exile (Full Art) Pokemon card from the Hidden Fates set. The card is displayed on a clear stand. The user is selling the card.
